   <body>
      <context>
         <p>If changes have been made to smart fields in the document, you can choose to reject these changes in the same session prior to check-in.</p>
         <p>To reject changes:</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Hover over the <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220124/49086829.png"
                      id="image_gmz_hsn_12c"/>
               <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol> button and select <uicontrol>Fields</uicontrol> to
               open the Document Panel.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         width="278"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/49086830.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Right-click on the changed field in the Document pane (highlighted in red) and
               select <uicontrol>Reject Changes</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="800"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/51576880.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
            <stepresult>
               <p>The field value is reverted to its previous value prior to the change. The
                  Document pane reloads to show the change.</p>
               <fig id="fig_jjk_j3q_12c">
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="800"
                         href="../attachments/45220124/51576881.png"
                         id="image_kjk_j3q_12c"/>
               </fig>
            </stepresult>
         </li>
      </ol>
